<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<section name="62">
	<p>
		To find out how well your investments have done,
		<random>
			<adjust god="The Three Fortunes" amount="1"/>
			<adjust codeword="Brush" amount="1"/>
			<adjust codeword="Eldritch" amount="2"/>
			<adjust codeword="Almanac" amount="3"/>
		</random>.
		Add 1 to the dice roll if you are an initiate of the Three Fortunes. Also add 1 if you have the codeword <i>Brush</i>, add 2 if you have the codeword <i>Eldritch</i>, and add 3 if you have the codeword <i>Almanac</i>.
	</p>
	<outcomes>
		<outcome range="2-4">
			<adjustmoney name="2.39" multiply="0">
				Lose entire sum invested
			</adjustmoney>
		</outcome>
		<outcome range="5-6">
			<adjustmoney name="2.39" multiply="0.5">
				Loss of 50%
			</adjustmoney>
		</outcome>
		<outcome range="7-8">
			<adjustmoney name="2.39" multiply="0.9">
				Loss of 10%
			</adjustmoney>
		</outcome>
		<outcome range="9-10">
			Investment remains unchanged
		</outcome>
		<outcome range="11-12">
			<adjustmoney name="2.39" multiply="1.1">
				Profit of 10%
			</adjustmoney>
		</outcome>
		<outcome range="13-14">
			<adjustmoney name="2.39" multiply="1.5">
				Profit of 50%
			</adjustmoney>
		</outcome>
		<outcome range="15+">
			<adjustmoney name="2.39" multiply="2">
				Double initial investment
			</adjustmoney>
		</outcome>
	</outcomes>
	<p>
		Now <goto section="39"/>, where you can withdraw the sum written in the box there after adjusting it according to the result rolled.
	</p>
</section>
